    "description": "《越野车机械师模拟器：初试锋芒》是《越野车机械师模拟器》的免费序章版本，它提供了一个完整的游戏体验，为玩家们提供三辆越野车以及森林赛道<br><br><strong>准备好开启越野车的冒险！</strong><br><br>在《越野车机械师》模拟器中挑战你的越野车维修技能，并为越野车将面对的最艰难的挑战做好准备！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/d42f82d985ecdd0435b93c9ba6cc1adf.poster.avif?t=1761041196\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/d42f82d985ecdd0435b93c9ba6cc1adf.webm?t=1761041196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/d42f82d985ecdd0435b93c9ba6cc1adf.mp4?t=1761041196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>接受那些远超正常维修水平的订单。客户的车辆将面对真正的越野挑战，你要为此做好准备，确保这些车辆能够经受得起超过它们原有能力的地形的折磨。如果你的顾客需要的话，记得安装更好的悬挂系统，或者加入一个通气管。但要注意选择那些不会超出你的预算的零件。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/d541ee8141c9d3fd8d7335cb8ef71807.poster.avif?t=1761041196\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/d541ee8141c9d3fd8d7335cb8ef71807.webm?t=1761041196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/d541ee8141c9d3fd8d7335cb8ef71807.mp4?t=1761041196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在单人任务中接受越野车维修的挑战！享受你的不断进步，你将会慢慢学会如何处理更加昂贵的车。购买额外的零件和工具，你要做得是将一辆车变为真正的越野怪兽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/cdc86507e52f2d45eaef5025315d8f43.poster.avif?t=1761041196\" width=598 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/cdc86507e52f2d45eaef5025315d8f43.webm?t=1761041196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387500/extras/cdc86507e52f2d45eaef5025315d8f43.mp4?t=1761041196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在越野冒险中测试你的车辆改装。穿越险峻的地形，攀爬陡峭的悬崖，穿越泥泞的河流。在前进到下一个障碍之前，享受激动人心的风景。当然，别忘记了在你把车交还给客户之前，做个彻底的清洗！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 改装各式不同的车辆<br></li><li> 优秀的画面<br></li><li> 多种多样的工具可供选择<br></li><li> 多样的零件选择，可让你的车呈现更好的状态<br></li><li> 故事性十足的职业模式<br></li><li> 各式随机分配的任务<br></li><li> 多样的装饰性元素<br></li><li> 丰富的赛道可供你测试越野性能<br></li><li> 无穷的乐趣</li></ul><br><br><br>官方QQ群：1070109603",
